%3EGiven%20its%20strong%20Democratic%20tilt%2C%20Biden%20is%20basically%20assured%20of%20winning%20Cook%20County%20%E2%80%94%20which%20includes%20Chicago%20and%20many%20of%20its%20suburbs%20%E2%80%94%20by%20an%20overwhelming%20margin%20this%20November.%20In%20the%202020%20election%2C%20Biden%20won%20more%20than%201.7%20million%20votes%20in%20Cook%20County%20compared%20to%20roughly%20558%2C000%20votes%20for%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Biden%20was%20on%20the%20ballot%20for%20a%20noncompetitive%20race%20where%20his%20nomination%20as%20the%20party's%20standard-bearer%20wasn't%20in%20question.%20(So%20far%2C%20Biden%20has%20won%20roughly%20427%2C000%20votes%20in%20Cook%20County.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbattleground-states-2024-presidential-election-road-white-house-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20swing-state%20cities%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Atlanta%2C%20Detroit%2C%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20Milwaukee%2C%20Philadelphia%2C%20and%20Phoenix%2C%20the%20vote%20margins%20that%20come%20out%20of%20these%20Democratic%20strongholds%20will%20be%20critical%20for%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchicago.suntimes.com%2Felections%2F2024%2F03%2F20%2Fchicago-voter-turnout-march-primary-warning-sign-biden-democratic-party%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20low%20primary%20turnout%20in%20Chicago%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20an%20indicator%20of%20looming%20issues%20that%20the%20Biden%20campaign%20will%20have%20to%20address%20in%20other%20cities%20to%20emerge%20victorious%20in%20November%2C%20according%20to%20top%20Democratic%20pollster%20Celinda%20Lake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIllinois%20is%20a%20state%20that%20has%20apparatus%20and%20really%20has%20deep%20roots%20in%20the%20community.%20I%20think%20they%20just%20weren't%20turned%20on%20for%20this%20election%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20warning%20sign%20to%20other%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20The%20Chicago%20Sun-Times'%