eople%20of%20PoK%20will%20merge%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Pakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif's%20recent%20remarks%20about%20Kashmir%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCan%20they%20ever%20take%20Kashmir%3F%20They%20should%20be%20worried%20about%20Pakistan-Occupied%20Kashmir.%20I%20had%20said%20almost%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20ago%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20need%20for%20us%20to%20attack%20and%20occupy%20because%20a%20situation%20is%20developing%20there%20that%20people%20of%20PoK%20themselves%20are%20demanding%20merger%20with%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20whether%20the%20government%20was%20making%20any%20plan%2C%20he%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20say%20anything%20more%2C%20I%20should%20not.%20We%20are%20not%20going%20to%20attack%20any%20country.%20India%20has%20a%20character%20of%20never%20attacking%20any%20country%20in%20the%20world%2C%20nor%20has%20it%20occupied%20an%20inch%20of%20other's%20territory.%20But%20PoK%20was%20ours%2C%20PoK%20is%20ours%2C%20and%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20PoK%20will%20itself%20merge%20with%20India.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20made%20the%20comments%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatvnews.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Faap-ki-adalat-rajnath-singh-tells-rajat-sharma-no-need-to-attack-people-of-pok-they-themselves-want-merger-with-india-2024-03-23-922914%5C%22%3E'%3Cem%3EAAP%20ki%20Adalat'%3C%2Fem%3E%20programme%20on%20India%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20February%2C%20a%20political%20activist%20from%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%2C%20Amjad%20Ayub%20Mirza%2C%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20people%20in%20PoK%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20Pakistani%20occupation%20and%20they%20are%20now%20demanding%20merger%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20released%20by%20him%2C%20activist%20Mirza%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20PoK%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20have%20told%20me%20that%20they%20now%20demand%20to%20be%20merged%20into%20India%2C%20as%20they%20are%20officially%20their%20citizens%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recent%20elections%20in%20Pakistan%20have%20just%20given%20us%20a%20fractured%20mandate.%20The%20upcoming%20elections%20will%20have%20a%20fruitful%20result%20for%20India%20but%20we%20the%20people%20of%20PoK%20ask%20that%2C%20for%20how%20long%20will%20we%20have%20to%20wait%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20Pakistan's%20oppression%20and%20get%20merged%20in%20India%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20PoK%20activist%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stated%20that%20India%20has%20a%20character%20of%20never%20attacking%20any%20nation%20and%20not%20occupying%20anyone's%20land.%20However%2C%20he%20asserted%20that%20India%20will%20give%20a%20befitting%20response%20if%20its%20prestige%20is%20attacked%20by%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20a%20possible%20scenario%20where%20China%20attacks%20India%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGod%20should%20give%20them%20the%20good%20sense%20not%20to%20commit%20such%20mistakes.%20India%20has%20a%20character%20of%20never%20attacking%20any%20country%2C%20but%20if%20any%20country%20attacks%20us%2C%20we%20do%20not%20spare%20them.%20But%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20if%20anyone%20asks%20us%2C%20we%20have%20good%20relations%20with%20all%20our%20neighbours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20maintain%20ties%20but%20not%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20India's%20self-respect.%20But%20if%20any%20country%20attacks%20India's%20prestige%2C%20it%20has%20the%20power%20to%20give%20it%20a%20befitting%20reply.%20We%20want%20to%20have%20good%20relations%20with%20neighbours%20because%20Atal%20ji%20used%20to%20say%20that%20we%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20we%20can%20change%20friends%20in%20life%20but%20neighbours%20never%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underlined%20that%20India%20will%20tackle%20any%20threat%20that%20arises%20from%20China%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20country%20has%20become%20a%20powerful%20nation%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20whether%20there%20was%20any%20threat%20from%20China%20now%2C%20the%20Defence%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20tackle%20if%20any%20threat%20arises%2C%20what's%20there%20in%20it.%20But%2C%20we%20cannot%20sit%20holding%20our%20heads%20in%20hands%20thinking%20about%20the%20threat.%20If%20the%20threat%20arises%2C%20it%20will%20be%20tackled.%20India%20is%20no%20more%20a%20weak%20country.%20India%20has%20become%20a%20powerful%20country%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20allegation%20that%20China%20has%20occupied%20nearly%202%2C000%20square%20kilometres%20of%20India's%20territory%2C%20he%20expressed%20sadness%20over%20his%20remarks%20and%20stated%20that%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20remind%20him%20about%20the%20activities%20China%20did%20in%201962.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20feeling%20really%20sad%20that%20he%20is%20questioning%20the%20valour%20of%20our%20jawans.%20He%20should%20not%20be%20making%20such%20remarks.%20How%20much%20territory%20was%20occupied%20by%20China%20in%201962%20and%20what%20activities%20have%20been%20done%20by%20China.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20remind%20him%20and%20do%20not%20talk%20about%20it.%20Rest%20assured%2C%20today%2C%20we%20can%20say%20that%20we%20will%20not%20like%20to%20lose%20even%20an%20inch%20of%20our%20territory.%20I%20cannot%20disclose%20much%20about%20the%20details%20because%20India%20and%20China%20are%20engaged%20in%20talks%2C%20and%20the%20talks%20are%20going%20on%20in%20a%20right%20manner.%20Talks%20are%20going%20on%20in%20a%20cordial%20atmosphere.%20Otherwise%2C%20I%20would%20have%20disclosed%20more%20details.%20Please%20do%20not%20compel%20me%20to%20disclose%20more.%20I%20cannot%20disclose%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20February%2C%20India%20and%20China%20held%20the%2021st%20round%20of%20Corps%20Commander%20level%20meeting%20on%20Monday%20at%20the%20Chushul-Moldo%20border%20to%20defuse%20tensions%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20nations%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20standoff%20since%20April-May%202020%20over%20the%20transgressions%20by%20the%20Chinese%20Army%20in%20multiple%20areas%20including%20the%20Finger%20area%2C%20Galwan%20Valley%2C%20Hot%20springs%2C%20and%20Kongrung%20Nala.%20The%20situation%20worsened%20after%20violent%20clashes%20with%20Chinese%20troops%20in%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20June%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraising%20the%20bravery%20of%20India's%20defence%20personnel%2C%20he%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20want%20to%20say%20that%20whatever%20happened%20with%20China%20this%20time%20too%2C%20I%20feel%20proud%20of%20the%20courage%20shown%20by%20soldiers%20of%20Indian%20Army%2C%20Air%20Force%20and%20Navy%20personnel.%20There%20are%20many%20such%20incidents%20that%20if%20countrymen%20are%20made%20aware%20of%20about%20the%20army%20of%20our%20country%2C%20their%20respect%20will%20increase%20further.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20fight%20between%20India%20and%20China%20in%20Galwan%2C%20he%20stated%20that%20India's%20soldiers%20did%20not%20fire%20a%20single%20shot%20and%20instead%20were%20engaged%20in%20a%20physical%20combat.%20He%20said%20India%20lost%2020%20soldiers%20during%20the%20fight.%20However%2C%20China%20did%20not%20disclose%20information%20regarding%20their%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20seen%20what%20happened%20in%20Galwan%20during%20our%20fight%20with%20China%2C%20our%20brave%20jawans%20did%20not%20fire%20a%20single%20shot%2C%20they%20were%20engaged%20in%20physical%20combat.%2020%20of%20our%20jawans%20were%20killed%2C%20and%20how%20many%20Chinese%20soldiers%20were%20killed%3F%20I%20am%20not%20saying%2C%20but%20foreign%20agency%20reports%20say%2035%20to%2040%20Chinese%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20clashes.%20We%20have%20not%20said%20anything%20related%20to%20China.%20We%20have%20accepted%20it%20that%2020%20of%20our%20jawans%20were%20killed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20true%20that%20China%20is%20carrying%20out%20infrastructure%20development%20near%20Line%20of%20Control%20at%20a%20fast%20pace%20since%20a%20long%20time.%26quot%3B%20He%20further%20said%20that%20Defence%20Minister%20during%20Congress%20government%20asked%20not%20to%20develop%20infrastructure%20on%20India-China%20border.%20He%20stated%20that%20India%20has%20started%20developing%20infrastructure%20at%20a%20fast%20pace%20after%20the%20Modi-led%20government%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Congress%20government%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20said%20that%20if%20we%20develop%20infrastructure%20on%20the%20India-China%20border%2C%20China%20will%20enter%20India%2C%20so%20do%20not%20develop%20infrastructure.%20After%20the%20Modi%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20we%20have%20also%20started%20developing%20infrastructure%20at%20a%20fast%20speed%20on%20border.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERefuting%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20claims%20that%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20fears%20China%2C%20he%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20surprised%20when%20somebody%20says%20Modiji%20Darte%20Hain.%20It%20is%20not%20in%20his%20nature%20to%20be%20afraid.%20There%20is%20nothing%20to%20be%20afraid%20of.%20The%20problem%20is%20these%20people%20do%20not%20understand.%20Why%20are%20they%20raising%20questions%20about%20India's%20strength%20and%20valour%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711291020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Frjb09p28_rajnath-singh_625x300_0