%2Fislamphobia-statecraft-assam-himanta-biswa-sarma%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Bengali-origin%20Muslims%20who%20are%20landless%20could%20not%20apply%20for%20land%20under%20this%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711283425000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23221556%2F2022_11img23_Nov_2022_PTI11_23_2022_000240B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fassam-pauses-noc-for-sale-of-land-between-people-of-different-religions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20cited%20inputs%20from%20intelligence%20agencies%20which%20have%20allegedly%20pointed%20to%20the%20transfer%20of%20land%20involving%20people%20of%20different%20religions%20'by%20fraudulent%20means'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fassam-pauses-noc-for-sale-of-land-between-people-of-different-religions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nigerian%20pupils%20taken%20in%20mass%20abduction%20freed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711283302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F33AA%2Fproduction%2F_132862231_nigeria.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68649221%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gunmen%20rode%20through%20the%20school%20in%20Kuriga%20in%20north-western%20Nigeria%20seizing%20children%20as%20young%20as%20eight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A365%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68649221%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68649221.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68649221.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kriti%20Sanon%20dating%20Kabir%20Bahia%3F%20Netizens%20speculate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22pu