an%2C%20Thirumalai%2C%20who%20sought%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20his%20brother%2C%20Ganesan%2C%20who%20had%20been%20missing%20from%20the%20Coimbatore%20centre%20since%20February%202023.%20That%20Ganesan%20was%20absent%20was%20informed%20to%20his%20brother%20by%20the%20Foundation%20itself%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirumalai%20noted%20that%20the%20Foundation%20lodged%20a%20police%20complaint%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20FIR%2C%20in%20the%20same%20month%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98yoga%20centre%E2%80%99%20at%20Coimbatore%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20of%20its%20outposts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20website%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20large%20residential%20facility%20houses%20an%20active%20international%20community%20of%20brahmacharis%2C%20full-time%20volunteers%20and%20visitors.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresented%20by%20Additional%20Public%20Prosecutor%20E.%20Raj%20Thilak%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20police%20indicated%20that%20an%20investigation%20was%20ongoing%20into%20the%20multiple%20people%20who%20had%20gone%20missing%20%E2%80%93%20some%20of%20whom%20it%20claimed%20may%20have%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20asked%20police%20to%20furnish%20a%20detailed%20status%20report%20on%20this%20investigation%20by%20April%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foundation%20has%20called%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20claim%20false.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20news%20claiming%20that%20six%20people%20have%20disappeared%20from%20Isha%20Yoga%20Center%20since%202016%20is%20totally%20false%20and%20baseless%2C%20debunks%20Isha%20Foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fsix-people-have-gone-missing-from-sadhgurus-isha-yoga-centre-since-2016-tamil-nadu-police-11711117054161.html%5C%22%3Ein%20an%20official%20statement.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrave%20allegations%20surround%20multiple%20centres%20of%20the%20Isha%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Jag