ual%20arts%20have%20transformed%20significantly.%20On%20the%20buoyant%20socio-political%20landscape%20has%20now%20surfaced%20a%20more%20systematically%20aspirational%20right-wing%20shadow%2C%20which%20only%20deepened%20concerns%20about%20dissent%20through%20art%20in%20contemporary%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECatalyzing%20the%20growth%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enukkad-naataks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20a%20prolific%20art-form%2C%20essential%20to%20Hashmi%E2%80%99s%20artistic%20politics%20was%20taking%20theatre%20from%20elite%20spaces%2C%20and%20politically%20and%20intricately%20bringing%20it%20into%20the%20common%20masses.%20Actor%20Naseeruddin%20Shah%20fondly%20introspects%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20upon%20his%20bewilderment%20of%20seeing%20how%20despite%20his%20thespian%20vigour%2C%20Hashmi%20chased%20neither%20fame%2C%20nor%20fortune%3B%20immersing%20himself%20in%20struggles%20of%20peasants%20and%20workers%2C%20as%20he%20found%20himself%20performing%20for%20and%20amidst%20them.%20In%20conceiving%20the%20Jana%20Natya%20Manch%20(The%20People%E2%80%99s%20Theatre)%20%E2%80%93%20wittily%20abbreviated%20to%20JANAM%20(Birth)%20%E2%80%93%20Hashmi%20responded%20to%20the%20ruling%20class%E2%80%99%20strategy%20for%20countering%20any%20claims%20against%20its%20oppression%2C%20as%20he%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20level%20of%20consciousness%20by%20propagating%20and%20strengthening%20all%20that%20is%20backward%2C%20obscurantist%2C%20and%20superstitious%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20then%2C%20Hashmi%20identified%20the%20ruling%20class%E2%80%99%20inclinations%20to%20narrowly%20appropriate%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdecolonisation%E2%80%9D%20narrative%3B%20something%20now%20often%20invoked%20in%20justifying%20exclusionary%20politics.%20While%20acknowledging%20the%20depth%20of%20traditional%20performing%20arts%2C%20Hashmi%20saw%20fissures%20in%20a%20puritanical%20approaches%20towards%20theatre%20in%20India%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20therefore%20devoted%20himself%20to%20developing%20a%20political%20art-form%20that%20secured%20a%20just%20future%20for%20the%20marginalized%2C%20instead%20of%20falling%20into%20the%20trappings%20of%20an%20unjust%20past.%20Up%20until%20his%20demise%2C%20JANAM%20performed%20for%20mass%20audiences%20under%20his%20de%20facto%20direction%2C%20engaging%20with%20the%20working%20class%20through%20thousands%20of%20performances%20carried%20out%20predominantly%20in%20working-class%20neighbourhoods%2C%20factories%20and%20workshops.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F22150416%2FDSbt8AwUMAEreXY.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F22150416%2FDSbt8AwUMAEreXY.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F22150416%2FDSbt8AwUMAEreXY-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F22150416%2FDSbt8AwUMAEreXY-1024x577.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-422300%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESafdar%20Hashmi%20performing%20with%20other%20JANAM%20members.%C2%A0Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20me%2C%20the%20current%20state%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20visual%20%E2%80%9Centertainment%E2%80%9D%20poses%20the%20question%20of%20Safdar%E2%80%99s%20significance.%20In%20a%20confluence%20of%20screen%20and%20stage%2C%20the%202010%E2%80%99s%20marked%20a%20shift%20in%20how%20film%2C%20theatre%E2%80%99s%20more%20modern%20and%20pervasive%20counterpart%2C%20would%20be%20%E2%80%98consumed%E2%80%99.%20It%20also%20birthed%20the%20%E2%80%98web-series%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20consequently%2C%20the%20run-of-the-mill%20Bollywood%20movie%E2%80%99s%20religion-like%20significance%20dwindled.%20Works%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGangs%20of%20Wasseypur%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESacred%20Games%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMirzapur%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ewere%20original%2C%20exciting%2C%20with%20realistic%20visuals.%20Amidst%20declining%20public%20interest%2C%20the%20Goliath%20Bollywood%20too%20was%20coerced%20into%20incorporating%20a%20some%20form%20of%20originality.%20Thus%20emerged%20a%20new%2C%20%E2%80%98theatre-bred%E2%80%99%20artist-class%20in%C2%A0%20the%20cinematic%20limelight.%20Actors%20who%20were%20%E2%80%98serious%E2%80%99%20rather%20than%20frivolous%20superstars.%20While%2C%20on%20the%20surface%2C%20this%20guaranteed%20a%20theatrical%20enrichment%20of%20mainstream%20filmmaking%2C%20not%20all%20has%20gone%20according%20to%20plan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20backdrop%20of%20heightened%20sentiments%20in%20this%20consciously%20orchestrated%20decade%2C%20commercialisation%20and%20regressive%20politics%20render%20this%20%E2%80%9Calternatively%20mainstream%E2%80%9D%20artist%20class%20as%20a%20conservative%20tool.%20Dominating%20Indian%20screens%20significantly%20today%2C%20it%20often%20forgets%20its%20roots%20and%20the%20true%20political%20role%20of%20the%20performing%20arts%20%E2%80%93%20striking%20down%20oppressive%20structures.%20While%20it%20is%20undeniable%20that%20many%20such%20artists%20contribute%20to%20meaningful%20and%20humane%20projects%2C%20to%20the%20observant%2C%20simultaneously%20criticising%20oppression%2C%20and%20partaking%20in%20projects%20that%20appeal%20to%20the%20ruling%20class%20reveals%20an%20escapist%20hypocrisy.%20This%20phenomenon%2C%20as%20Hashmi%20himself%20identified%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20new%20but%20as%20India%20witnesses%20unprecedented%20social%20polarisation%2C%20it%20must%20draw%20conscious%20critical%20attention.%20This%20is%20simply%20because%20its%20danger%20lies%20in%20its%20effectiveness.%20It%20is%20clear%20how%20narratives%20of%20exploitation%20and%20discrimination%20become%20more%20palatable%20to%20the%20masses%20when%20artists%20with%20a%20theatrical%20background%20(or%20even%20otherwise)%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20who%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20their%20craft%20seriously%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20are%20associated%20with%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20must%20remind%20oneself%20that%20Hashmi%20and%20his%20legacy%20are%20now%20more%20relevant%20than%20ever%2C%20with%20intensifying%20right-wing%20politics%2C%20and%20this%20unique%20artist-class%E2%80%99%20tendency%20to%20absolve%20themselves%20of%20artistic%20responsibilities%20towards%20the%20oppressed.%20A%20recent%20example%20is%20a%20podcast%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20discussing%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%E2%80%99s%20soulless%20and%20gratuitously%20violent%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAnimal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20featuring%20prominent%20alternative%20artists%2C%20including%20Manoj%20Bajpayee%2C%20Nawazuddin%20Siddiqui%2C%20Arshad%20Warsi%20and%20Aparshakti%20Khurana.%20Citing%20artistic%20license%2C%20and%20their%20%E2%80%9Csubjective%20moralities%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20almost%20unanimously%20denied%20any%20artistic%20responsibility%2C%20with%20Khurana%20even%20seeing%20merit%20in%20the%20film%20since%20it%20made%20him%20%E2%80%9Cforget%20his%20moral%20compass%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20Bajpayee%20laughing%20off%20cinema%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20shaping%20public%20morality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fsafdar-hashmi-halla-bol-sudhanva-deshpande%5C%22%3EThe%20Untimely%20Death%20of%20Playwright%20Activist%20Safdar%20Hashmi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20lacerate%2C%20or%20allow%20comfort%20in%20lacerating%20an%20artist%E2%80%99s%20moral%20fabric%2C%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20%E2%80%9Cobjectivity%E2%80%9D%20is%20to%20murder%20their%20conscience%20and%20it%20is%20here%20that%20we%20must%20remember%20Hashmi%20and%20his%20belief%20in%20tangible%20action.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20intention-centric%20is%20to%20deny%20the%20world%20of%20action%20altogether%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20%E2%80%9CThe%20mill%20owner%20may%20claim%20that%20he%20does%20not%20wish%20to%20exploit%20his%20workers.%20But%20shall%20we%20judge%20him%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20his%20alleged%20intentions%20or%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20his%20actions%3F%E2%80%9D%20Today%2C%20the%20same%20applies%20to%20this%20artist-class%2C%20whose%20intentions%20and%20actions%20transpire%20in%20polar%20contradictions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20circling%20back%20to%20Hashmi%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20one%20must%20remember%20his%20devotion%20to%20%E2%80%9Cduties%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20performer.%20He%20sacrificed%20his%20life%2C%20not%20merely%20to%20secure%20the%20freedom%2C%20but%20to%20exercise%20it%20responsibly%20and%20for%20the%20oppressed%2C%20teaching%20others%20the%20same.%20So%20how%20might%20have%20his%20life%20unfurled%20today%3F%20Would%20he%20be%20staging%20plays%20in%20critique%20of%20waning%20democracy%20like%20he%20did%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CKursi%2C%20Kursi%2C%20Kursi%E2%80%9D%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EWould%20he%20critique%20rising%20prices%20and%20privatisation%2C%20as%20he%20did%20with%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDTC%20Ki%20Dhandhli%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%3F%20Perhaps%20he%20would%20call%20for%20attention%20towards%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20crisis%2C%20or%20the%20denial%20of%20marital%20rights%20to%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community.%20Would%20he%20perhaps%20be%20silenced%20as%20he%20was%20thirty-five%20years%20ago%2C%20all%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20his%20ideals%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20certainty%20is%20that%20he%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20emerge%20an%20opportunist%20in%20a%20visual%20pseudo-renaissance%2C%20absolving%20himself%20of%20reformative%20responsibility%20and%20ratifying%20oppression.%20The%20likes%20of%20him%20are%20devoted%20in%20establishing%20a%20world%20with%20true%20%E2%80%9Cobjective%E2%80%9D%20fairness%2C%20as%20JANAM%20continues%20to%20do%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20And%20while%20Hashmi%20created%20in%20a%20language%20often%20imposed%20on%20others%2C%20for%20one%20to%20seek%20him%20only%20within%20its%20folds%20would%20perhaps%20be%20an%20injustice.%20In%20my%20life%20anchored%20in%20the%20complexities%20of%20Northeast%20India%2C%20Hashmi%20also%20speaks%20in%20tongues%20long%20drowned%20out%20by%20Bollywood%E2%80%99s%20loudness%3B%20emerging%20in%20works%20like%20Jaicheng%20Jai%20Dohutia%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Handuk%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(Assamese%2FMoran%20%E2%80%93%202016)%20which%20grippingly%20depicts%20lives%20in%20Assam%20arrested%20by%20hyper-militarisation%20and%20secessionist%20conflict%3B%20or%20Haobam%20Paban%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20vignettes%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20political%20crises%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENine%20Hills%20and%20One%20Valley%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(Manipuri%20and%20Tangkhul%20%E2%80%93%202022).%20He%20similarly%20emerges%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20calling%20out%20injustice%20in%20the%20many%20languages%20that%20we%20speak.%20And%20while%20such%20works%20frequently%20find%20critical%20acclaim%2C%20the%20irony%20of%20contemporary%20%E2%80%98pan%E2%80%99-Indian%20cinema%20is%20that%20its%20cultural%20and%20commercial%20hegemonies%20still%20limit%20their%20access%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20masses.%20The%20truth%20remains%20however%2C%20that%20the%20likes%20of%20Safdar%20Hashmi%20are%20still%20sharing%20stories%20with%20a%20clean%20conscience.%20And%20we%2C%20as%20citizens%2C%20have%20the%20moral%20responsibility%20to%20listen%2C%20for%20only%20then%20will%20art%20serve%20its%20true%20purpose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20only%20that%20is%20a%20tribute%20befitting%20his%20legacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EAyaan%20Halder%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20legal%20scholar%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Law%2C%20Gauhati%20University%2C%20Guwahati%2C%20Assam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711272647000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F22150641%2Fcollage-8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fthirty-five-years-after-he-was-killed-safdar-hashmis-legacy-still-remains-alive%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Unlike%20many%20other%20theatre%20artists%20in%20films%2C%20Hashmi%20would%20have%20uncompromisingly%C2%A0staged%20plays%20on%20current%20political%20topics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fthirty-five-years-after-he-was-killed-safdar-hashmis-legacy-still-remains-alive%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20'Lootere'%2C%20Hansal%20Mehta%20and%20Team%20Venture%20Into%20the%20Piracy-Infested%20Waters%20Off%20Somalia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F24144608%2FScreenshot-2024-03-24-at-2.44.03%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Shaailesh%20R.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELootere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20an%20eight%20episode%20mini-series%20on%20Disney%2BHotstar%2C%20it%20almost%20always%20appears%20like%20its%20anti-hero%20central%20figure%2C%20Vikrant%20Gandhi%20(played%20by%20Vivek%20Gomber)%2C%20talks%20big%20game%20without%20the%20depth%20for%20any%20of%20it.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20reckless%20manner%20in%20which%20he%20lights%20up%20a%20cigarette%20like%20he%E2%80%99s%20starring%20in%20his%20own%20Nicholas%20Cage%20movie%2C%20or%20the%20way%20he%20suddenly%20goes%20from%20greeting%20his%20business%20partners%20to%20threatening%20them%2C%20making%20one%20want%20to%20reach%20out%20into%20the%20screen%20and%20tell%20him%20to%20be%20more%20cautious.%20But%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20the%20ground%20is%20shrinking%20beneath%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F4cu-eB_9AKk%3Fsi%3DkapUwRGKjfTffQeI%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20the%20son-in-law%20of%20the%20unofficial%20%E2%80%98king%E2%80%99%20of%20Somalia%2C%20Gandhi%20is%20now%20shown%20to%20be%20managing%20an%20empire%20well%20into%20its%20dusk.%20Like%20any%20other%20vain%20man%20in%20his%20shoes%2C%20he%20thinks%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20one%20business%20deal%20that%20will%20turn%20it%20all%20around.%20Gandhi%20seems%20like%20a%20guy%20who%20knows%20a%20lucrative%20idea%20when%20he%20sees%20one%2C%20but%20without%20the%20patience%20to%20see%20it%20through.%20He%20walks%20around%20with%20a%20chip%20on%20his%20shoulder%2C%20something%20that%20feels%20even%20more%20significant%20when%20you%20think%20about%20the%20journey%20of%20the%20actor%20playing%20it.%20Gomber%20has%20been%20acting%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20but%20without%20that%20one%20role%20that%20makes%20him%20a%20known%20face%20among%20the%20masses.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20until%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFeaturing%20Hansal%20Mehta%20as%20showrunner%20and%20directed%20by%20Jai%20Mehta%2C%20desperation%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20actual%20protagonist%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELootere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Set%20in%20Somalian%20waters%20in%202016%2C%20a%20cargo%20ship%20is%20hijacked%20by%20pirates.%20The%20hostage%20drama%20gradually%20evolves%20into%20a%20multi-dimensional%20chess%20game%2C%20where%20each%20of%20the%20players%20are%20battling%20dire%20circumstances%20for%20survival.%20There%E2%80%99s%20the%20ship%20crew%20who%20are%20obviously%20affected%20by%20the%20hijack%2C%20but%20writers%20Vishal%20Kapoor%20and%20Suparn%20S%20Varma%20(based%20on%20a%20story%20by%20Anshuman%20Singh)%20don%E2%80%99t%20skimp%20on%20empathy%20for%20the%20pirates%2C%20smugglers%2C%20the%20corrupt%20politicians%20trying%20to%20elbow%20Gandhi%20out%20of%20the%20Mogadishu%20port%20presidential%20elections%2C%20and%20also%20terrorists%20for%20whom%20Gandhi%20is%20shipping%20some%20sensitive%20cargo.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELootere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20all%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20a%20frenetic%20Hollywood%20thriller%2C%20something%20Jai%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20filmmaking%20choices%20reflect.%20Different%20plot-points%20in%20the%20show%20are%20reminiscent%20of%20Ridley%20Scott%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBlack%20Hawk%20Down%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2001)%2C%20Andrew%20Niccol%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELord%20of%20War%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2005)%2C%20Edward%20Zwick%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBlood%20Diamond%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2006)%2C%20Paul%20Greengrass%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECaptain%20Phillips%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2013)%20and%20even%20Michael%20Bay%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E13%20Hours%3A%20The%20Secret%20Soldiers%20of%20Benghazi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2016).%20Despite%20seeming%20derivative%20in%20portions%2C%20the%20series%20becomes%20its%20own%20heady%20cocktail%20of%20references%2C%20tropes%2C%20and%20catches%20you%20off%20guard%20with%20its%20astute%20observation%20of%20the%20bigger%20picture%20more%20than%20once.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20is%20up%20for%20re-election%20as%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Mogadishu%20port%20trust%2C%20which%20is%20a%20key%20ingredient%20for%20his%20influence%20in%20Somalia%E2%80%99s%20political%20circles.%20Everything%20suggests%20he%20might%20end%20up%20on%20the%20losing%20side.%20He%20has%20a%20consignment%20coming%20in%20for%20the%20Al-Muharib%20terror%20group%2C%20who%20plan%20to%20instigate%20civil%20war%20in%20the%20country.%20When%20others%20get%20wind%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20secret%20business%20deal%2C%20the%20responsibility%20falls%20on%20Gandhi%20himself%20to%20keep%20the%20ship%20away%20from%20Mogadishu.%20He%20hires%20someone%20to%20put%20the%20hijacking%20into%20motion%2C%20but%20what%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20simple%20in-and-out%20job%20becomes%20even%20more%20complex%20as%20the%20series%20goes%20on.%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20right-hand%20man%2C%20Gupta%20(Chirag%20Vora)%20is%20mistreated%20more%20than%20once%2C%20always%20keeping%20us%20guessing%20about%20whether%20he%20will%20shift%20sides%20when%20the%20time%20comes.%20Vikrant%20Gandhi%20reminded%20me%20of%20a%20phrase%20I%20heard%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBlood%20Diamond%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20when%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%E2%80%99s%20diamond%20smuggler%20character%20called%20himself%20a%20%E2%80%98soldier%20of%20fortune%E2%80%99.%20Gandhi%20is%20a%20short-fused%20guy%2C%20who%20always%20acts%20faster%20than%20he%20thinks%20and%20Gomber%E2%80%99s%20performance%20can%20seem%20almost%20amateurish.%20But%20then%20I%20noticed%20the%20performance%20within%20the%20performance%2C%20where%20Gomber%20puts%20on%20the%20swagger%20and%20confidence%20of%20a%20man%20who%20owns%20the%20world%20even%20while%20he%E2%80%99s%20in%20quicksand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F24144557%2FScreenshot-2024-03-24-at-2.44.14%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x563.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F24144557%2FScreenshot-2024-03-24-at-2.44.14%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x563.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F24144557%2FScreenshot-2024-03-24-at-2.44.14%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x165.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F24144557%2FScreenshot-2024-03-24-at-2.44.14%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703048%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22462%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20the%20trailer%20of%20%E2%80%98Lootera%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20shipping%20crew%20is%20a%20sensational%20bunch%20of%20actors%2C%20including%20Rajat%20Kapoor%20as%20the%20captain%20A.K%20Singh.%20Unlike%20Tom%20Hanks%E2%80%99%20emotionally-intelligent%20performance%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECaptain%20Phillips%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20where%20he%20gives%20the%20impression%20of%20being%20amenable%20to%20the%20pirates%2C%20I%20liked%20how%20Kapoor%20remains%20true%20to%20himself%20by%20going%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction.%20A.K%20Singh%20is%20the%20leader%20here%2C%20and%20the%20power%20and%20responsibility%20hangs%20over%20him%20even%20in%20his%20silences%20while%20he%E2%80%99s%20doing%20nothing.%20One%20can%20see%20Kapoor%20computing%20the%20consequence%20of%20each%20and%20every%20word%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20his%20mouth%2C%20or%20any%20action%20he%20takes.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20Pakistani%20crew%20member%2C%20who%20is%20conveniently%20shown%20to%20be%20the%20only%20self-serving%20one%20which%20I%20found%20slightly%20odd.%20Naina%20Sareen%20is%20brilliant%20in%20a%20brief%20role%20as%20the%20other%20engineer%20on%20deck%2C%20Aisha%2C%20who%20is%20subjected%20to%20the%20inappropriate%20advances%20of%20the%20pirates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20also%20liked%20the%20in-fighting%20within%20the%20pirates%2C%20with%20the%20seeds%20of%20despondency%20being%20sown%20by%20the%20lieutenant%20in%20the%20group.%20Slowly%20and%20steadily%2C%20as%20the%20hijack%20and%20the%20several%20rounds%20of%20negotiation%20begin%20to%20take%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20crew%20members%2C%20even%20the%20pirates%20begin%20to%20unravel.%20A%20surprise%20visit%20by%20the%20commander%20of%20the%20Al%20Muharib%20makes%20matters%20even%20more%20complicated.%20What%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20simple%20in-and-out%20operation%2C%20becomes%20a%20two-week%20ordeal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENothing%20captures%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELootere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20cosmopolitan%20tastes%20quite%20like%20Achint%20Thakkar%E2%80%99s%20music%20in%20the%20opening%20credits%20of%20each%20episode%20in%20the%20show.%20It%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20Afro-pop%2C%20but%20also%20manages%20to%20weave%20in%20the%20sound%20of%20%E2%80%9870s%20Salim-Javed%20noirs%20%E2%80%93%20evoking%20images%20of%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20sporting%20crisp%20suits%2C%20sunglasses%2C%20profusely%20smoking%20cigarettes%20while%20overlooking%20deals%20of%20smuggled%20gold%20biscuits.%20The%20action%20sequences%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELootere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20the%20focus%20and%20momentum%20that%20Mehta%20Sr%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFaraaz%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20might%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20leap%20for%20some%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20call%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELootere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20the%20more%20well-rounded%20cousin%20of%20Hansal%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EScam%201992%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EScam%202003%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20one%E2%80%99s%20slightly%20less%20in%20awe%20of%20its%20protagonist%2C%20even%20as%20he%20goes%20around%20trying%20to%20perform%20miracles%20out%20of%20thin%20air.%20The%20show%20also%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20shy%20away%20from%20showing%20him%20in%20a%20less-than-flattering%20light%2C%20especially%20in%20scenes%20where%20the%20son%20overhears%20his%20parents%20shouting%20abuses%20at%20each%20other%20during%20a%20particularly%20tense%20phone%20call.%20And%20therefore%2C%20the%20tragedy%20that%20befalls%20most%20of%20the%20characters%20feels%20earned%2C%20rather%20than%20simply%20being%20literary%20vindication.%20After%20all%2C%20desperation%20is%20the%20only%20language%20universally%20understood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20two%20episodes%20of%20Lootere%20are%20streaming%20on%20Disney%2BHotstar%2C%20the%20rest%20will%20be%20dropped%20once%20a%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711271997000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F24144608%2FScreenshot-2024-03-24-at-2.44.03%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Flootere-hansal-mehta-somalia-disney-hotstar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Often%2C%20the%20show%20catches%20the%20viewer%20off-guard%2C%20with%20occasional%20touches%20of%20a%20Hollywood%20thriller.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Flootere-hansal-mehta-somalia-disney-hotstar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bajaj%20Auto%20to%20invest%20over%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore%20in%20finance%20arm%20BACL%3A%20Official%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711271990000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F24%2Ffull%2F1711271910-0043.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%