0jokes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmadgaon-express-kunal-kemmu-film-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kejriwal's%20Arrest%20Takes%20India%20From%20the%20Rule%20of%20Law%20into%20the%20Rule%20of%20a%20Tyrant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F24110738%2FUntitled-design-5-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20arrest%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20hugely%20popular%20serving%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20crossed%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elakshman%20rekha%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20that%20uncrossable%2C%20invisible%20line%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ebetween%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Rule%20of%20Law%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20a%20tyrant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20been%20edging%20towards%20this%2C%20step%20by%20step%2C%20ever%20since%20he%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20with%20his%20third%20election%20battle%20imminent%2C%20he%20has%20finally%20crossed%20the%20line.%20Modi%20had%20shown%20scant%20regard%20for%20this%20line%20even%20when%20he%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20where%20he%20shored%20up%20his%20popularity%20by%20constantly%20stoking%20communal%20tension%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20has%20used%20democracy%20to%20capture%20power%20%E2%80%93%20only%20in%20order%20to%20destroy%20it.%20Hitler%20had%20done%20the%20same%20thing%20in%20Germany%20in%201933%2C%20Mohammed%20Morsi%20in%20Egypt%20in%202012%2C%20and%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdo%C4%9Fan%20in%20Turkey%20in%202016.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20moved%20cautiously%20during%20his%20first%20term%20in%20office%2C%20consolidating%20his%20none-too-strong%20support%20base%20within%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20by%20taking%20up%20long%20cherished%20programmes%20of%20the%20latter%20such%20as%20the%20crusade%20against%20the%20bogey%20of%20love%20jihad%2C%20the%20ruse%20of%20%3Cem%3Eghar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ewapsi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20law%20to%20abolish%20triple%20talaq.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20second%20term%2C%20he%20pushed%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20the%20abolition%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%20under%20Article%20370%20in%202019%20and%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%20for%20all%20Indians%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20religious%20affiliation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20achievements%20should%20have%20sufficed%2C%20but%20paranoia%20is%20an%20incurable%20condition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%20Modi%20won%20303%20seats%20against%20282%20in%202014%2C%20making%20the%20BJP%20the%20first%20non-Congress%20dominant%20party%20in%20the%20Indian%20political%20system.%20But%20this%20did%20not%20assuage%20his%20gnawing%20insecurity.%20In%20the%20succeeding%20four%20years%20he%20turned%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20and%20above%20all%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20into%20weapons%20for%20use%20against%20the%20leaders%20of%20all%20the%20main%20opposition%20parties%2C%20giving%20them%20the%20choice%20of%20being%20sent%20to%20jail%20without%20trial%20and%20with%20little%20hope%20of%20bail%2C%20often%20without%20framing%20a%20single%20actual%20charge%20against%20them%20that%20they%20could%20bring%20to%20a%20court%20of%20law%2C%20or%20joining%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-great-crossover-opposition-leaders-who-joined-the-bjp-after-action-by-central-agencies%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Great%20Crossover%3A%20Opposition%20Leaders%20Who%20Joined%20the%20BJP%20After%20Action%20by%20Central%20Agencies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20this%20stratagem%2C%20Modi%20broke%20one%20opposition%20party%20after%20the%20other%2C%20till%20there%20were%20only%20regional%20parties%20left%20relatively%20unscathed.%20The%20sole%20exceptions%20were%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20Bengal%2C%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%20Now%20Modi%20has%20turned%20his%20guns%20upon%20these%20last%20holdouts%20for%20democracy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20that%20was%20not%20their%20intention%2C%20by%20answering%20the%20summons%20of%20the%20ED%20and%20allowing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fed-conducting-raids-on-national-herald-headquarter-1982768-2022-08-02%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethemselves%20to%20be%20questioned%20for%20over%20several%20hours%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20have%20implicitly%20accepted%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20supremacy.%20Now%20Modi%20has%20turned%20his%20guns%20on%20the%20last%20but-one%20holdout%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKejriwal%20has%20fought%20Modi%20tooth%20and%20nail%20since%20his%20first%20day%20in%20office%20after%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20sensational%20victory%20in%202015%2C%20in%20which%20it%20garnered%2053%25%20of%20the%20votes%20and%20won%2067%20out%20of%2070%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20seats.%20To%20further%20sharpen%20the%20contrast%20between%20itself%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20AAP%20has%20projected%20an%20image%20of%20having%20done%20a%20lot%20for%20the%20people%20with%20little%20money.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20Modi%20this%20was%20unacceptable.%20Since%20then%20Kejriwal%20has%20been%20his%20b%C3%AAte%20noire%2C%20to%20be%20destroyed%20by%20any%20means%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-hounding-of-the-aam-aadmi-party%5C%22%3EAs%20I%20have%20noted%20before%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20new%20liquor%20policy%20%E2%80%93%20the%20case%20over%20which%20Kejriwal%20is%20arrested%20%E2%80%93%20made%20the%20government%20%3Cem%3Eget%20out%20of%20the%20liquor%20trade%20altogether%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20government%20decided%20the%20number%20of%20retail%20locations%20and%20principalities%20in%20each%20zone%20and%20put%20these%20up%20for%20auction.%20The%20retail%20locations%20were%20evenly%20spaced%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20mohalla%2C%20and%20every%20section%20of%20the%20population%2C%20had%20equal%20access%20to%20a%20liquor%20shop.%20It%20then%20auctioned%20the%20liquor%20shop%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20auction%2C%20the%20government%20garnered%20Rs%205%2C300%20crore%20from%20the%20auction%20of%20locations%20in%20the%20more%20affluent%2020%20zones%2C%20and%20Rs%203%2C180%20crore%20from%20the%20auctions%20in%20the%20remaining%2012%20zones.%20The%20lower%20paying%20capacity%20of%20the%20poorer%20areas%20was%20automatically%20reflected%20in%20the%20lower%20bids%20for%20these%20locations.%20The%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-excise-revenue-set-to-double-after-licence-auctions-under-new-liquor-policy-101628274483032.html%5C%22%3Eexpected%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20garner%20over%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20a%20year%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20liquor%20in%20the%20capital.%20This%20was%20almost%20double%20the%20average%20of%20Rs%205%2C500-crore%20recorded%20in%20the%20previous%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20entire%20liquor%20trade%20was%20privatised%2C%20and%20all%20allotments%20were%20made%20through%20public%20auction%2C%20where%20did%20the%20space%20remain%20for%20graft%20and%20favouritism%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20godi%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Emedia%20are%20putting%20the%20blame%20on%20Kejriwal%20for%20his%20arrest.%20If%20the%20Gandhis%20were%20willing%20to%20suffer%20hours%20of%20interrogation%2C%20why%20did%20Kejriwal%20refuse%20to%20heed%20seven%20summons%20from%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%3F%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20reason%20should%20have%20been%20obvious%3A%20he%20was%20elected%20by%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20to%20govern%20them%20and%20look%20after%20their%20welfare.%20Within%20the%20sphere%20of%20his%20duties%20he%20had%20done%20so.%20In%20matters%20that%20did%20not%20involve%20policing%20law%20and%20order%2C%20he%20did%20not%20have%20to%20answer%20to%20any%20higher%20authority%20than%20the%20people%20who%20elected%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKejriwal%E2%80%99s%20courage%20in%20confronting%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20tyranny%20has%20provided%20a%20torch%20with%20which%20to%20light%20the%20fire%20of%20battle%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20democratic%20India.%20And%20it%20seems%20as%20if%20non-BJP%20parties%20are%20responding.%20The%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20in%20Odisha%20has%20decided%20against%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%20The%20INDIA%20coalition%20has%20sprung%20to%20life%20again%20in%20defence%20of%20Kejriwal.%20What%20is%20more%20important%20is%20that%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20Alliance%20have%20realised%20at%20last%20that%20the%20crucial%20challenge%20before%20them%20is%20not%20the%20allocation%20of%20seats%20in%20each%20state%20but%20the%20framing%20of%20a%20national%20policy%20that%20will%20give%20the%20assurance%20of%20jobs%2C%20and%20greater%20job%20security%20to%20the%2080%20million%20persons%20who%20have%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20labour%20force%20in%20sheer%20despair%20after%20the%20onset%20of%20global%20recession%20in%202010-11%20when%20they%20rejoin%20the%20labour%20force.%20Modi%20has%20found%20no%20solution.%20That%20is%20why%20he%20has%20fallen%20back%20on%20stirring%20communal%20prejudice%20and%20animosity%20to%20shore%20up%20his%20support%20base%20for%20the%20next%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20victory%20that%20he%20expects%20in%20June%20will%20enable%20him%20to%20achieve%20this%20lifelong%20ambition%20%E2%80%93%20to%20get%20there%20he%20has%20been%20destroying%20every%20constitutional%20safeguard%20that%20Indian%20governments%20and%20lawmakers%20have%20painstakingly%20created%20since%20the%20first%20day%20of%20Independence.%20Only%20a%20united%20opposition%20that%20uses%20every%20medium%20to%20reach%20the%20people%20and%20inform%20them%20of%20the%20danger%20they%20are%20in%2C%20will%20suffice.%20Even%20then%20one%20can%20only%20hope%20that%20it%20will%20not%20be%20too%20little%2C%20too%20late.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fprem-shankar-jha%5C%22%3EPrem%20Shankar%20Jha%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711258747000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F24110738%2FUntitled-design-5-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrest-modi-rule-of-law%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Only%20a%20united%20opposition%20that%20uses%20every%20medium%20to%20reach%20the%20people%20and%20inform%20them%20of%20the%20danger%20they%20are%20in%2C%20will%20help.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrest-modi-rule-of-law%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Does%20the%20ISIS%20Attack%20on%20Russia%20Mean%20for%20Global%20Terrorism%20Threats%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F24104845%2FScreenshot-2024-03-24-at-10.48.32%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20appears%20almost%20certain%20the%20brutal%20assault%20on%20a%20Russian%20crowd%20settling%20down%20to%20watch%20a%20rock%20concert%20in%20M