%20ISIS-K%20operatives%20on%20multiple%20occasions.%20After%20years%20of%20warnings%20that%20Islamic%20State%20was%20rebuilding%20the%20capacity%20and%20resolve%20to%20resume%20an%20international%20terrorist%20campaign%2C%20Friday%E2%80%99s%20attack%20shows%20the%20threat%20is%20immediate%20and%20substantial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20US%2C%20together%20with%20five%20other%20nations%2C%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F03%2F22%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fisis-moscow-attack-concert-hall.html%3Fsmid%3Durl-share%5C%22%3Eshared%3C%2Fa%3E%20intelligence%20they%20had%20of%20ISIS-K%20planning%20for%20attacks%20in%20Moscow.%20But%20these%20warnings%20were%2C%20as%20recently%20as%20last%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F03%2F22%2Feurope%2Fcrocus-moscow-shooting%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Erejected%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20the%20Kremlin%20as%20being%20part%20of%20an%20attempt%20to%20discredit%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20comes%20at%20the%20worst%20possible%20moment%20for%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20despotic%20leader%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20his%20successful%20%E2%80%9Celection%20campaign%E2%80%9D%20to%20claim%20a%20mandate%20for%20a%20further%20six%20years%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20perhaps%20for%20this%20reason%20that%20Putin%E2%80%99s%20five-minute%20televised%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F03%2F23%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fmoscow-attack-putin.html%5C%22%3Eaddress%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday%2C%20in%20which%20he%20directed%20blame%20toward%20Ukraine%2C%20came%20so%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20yet%20know%20whether%20the%20Kremlin%20will%20continue%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDAlperovitch%2Fstatus%2F1771461905053360366%5C%22%3Eblame%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ukraine%20or%20the%20West%20for%20the%20attack%2C%20or%20if%20it%20will%20pivot%20to%20accept%20Islamic%20State%20was%20res