20and%20Caste%20Census%20(SECC)%20website%20has%20been%20down%20for%20more%20than%20two%20months%20now%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsocio-economic-caste-census-website-out-of-order-9229120%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20March%2022.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20media%20house%20contacted%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%20Development%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20maintaining%20the%20portal%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ministry%20quoted%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%20reasons%E2%80%9D%20and%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20making%20%E2%80%9Call%20out%20efforts%E2%80%9D%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20website%20is%20live%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202011%2C%20India%20conducted%20the%20Socio%20Economic%20and%20Caste%20Census%2C%20its%20first-ever%20caste-based%20census%20since%201931.%20The%20census%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20the%20first%20paperless%20census%2C%20conducted%20on%20hand-held%20electronic%20devices%20by%20the%20government%20in%20640%20districts%20%E2%80%94%20showed%20that%20one%20out%20of%20three%20families%20living%20in%20villages%20is%20landless%20and%20depends%20on%20manual%20labour%20for%20their%20livelihood%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EPTI%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Findicators%2Fsocio-economic-and-caste-census-paints-grim-rural-picture-to-help-improve-social-schemes%2Farticleshow%2F47930341.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20revealed%20the%20poor%20state%20of%20education%20in%20rural%20India%2C%20with%20the%20finding%20that%20nearly%20one-fourth%20of%20families%20have%20no%20literate%20adult%20above%20the%20age%20of%2025%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20aim%20of%20the%20census%20was%20for%20the%20government%20to%20improve%20various%20social%20welfare%20schemes%20%E2%80%94%20including%20to%20identify%20beneficiaries%20of%20schemes%20such%20as%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Pradhan%20Mantri%2C%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20and%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awaas%20Yojana-Gramin%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIE%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%20%E2%80%94%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20economically%20backward%20communities%20including%20people%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Castes%2C%20using%20the%20data%20it%20generated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20crucial%20data%2C%20however%2C%20is%20no%20longer%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20reported%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20March%2022.%20Per%20the%20news%20report%2C%20the%20portal%20has%20been%20down%20at%20least%20since%20January%206%2C%202024%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20when%20the%20Internet%20archive%E2%80%99s%20wayback%20machine%20last%20captured%20snapshots%20of%20the%20census%20portal.%20As%20of%20the%20time%20this%20story%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20also%20written%20on%20March%2023%2C%20the%20website%20was%20still%20down.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%20that%20when%20it%20contacted%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%20Development%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20maintaining%20the%20portal%20%E2%80%94%20the%20news%20house%20was%20told%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20an%20outage%20of%20the%20SECC%20website%20due%20to%20technical%20reasons%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9C%5BThe%5D%20Ministry%20is%20making%20all%20out%20efforts%20to%20make%20the%20web-site%20live%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20ministry%20source%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIE%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reported%20that%20unnamed%20sources%20said%20that%20the%20issue%20was%20flagged%20during%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20internal%20meetings%20at%20least%20twice%20since%20January%20this%20year.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20one%20such%20meeting%20on%20January%2024%2C%20it%20was%20noted%20that%20the%20AMC%20(annual%20maintenance%20contract)%20for%20SECC%20hardware%20had%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Crenewed%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIE%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported.%20Sources%20also%20revealed%2C%20per%20the%20news%20report%2C%20that%20the%20SECC%20servers%20were%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Crestored%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20week%2C%E2%80%9D%20on%20February%206.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECaste%20censuses%20have%20been%20a%20crucial%20election%20issue%20in%20many%20states%2C%20precisely%20for%20the%20data%20that%20emerge%20from%20it.%20In%20October%20last%20year%2C%20Bihar%20conducted%20its%20first%20ever%20state-based%20caste%20census.%20The%20census%20found%20that%20dominant%20castes%20make%20up%20just%2015.5%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20while%20its%20marginalised%20castes%20comprise%2084%25.%20It%20also%20found%20that%20about%2094%20lakh%20families%20%E2%80%94%2034.13%25%20of%20the%20total%202.76%20crore%20families%20in%20Bihar%20%E2%80%93%20are%20economically%20poor%20and%20earn%20less%20than%20Rs%206%2C000%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0basically%2C%20every%20third%20family%20was%20poor.%20Based%20on%20this%20data%2C%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnitish-kumar-socio-economic-data-caste-survey-poverty-assistance%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannounced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20slew%20of%20measures%20targeted%20at%20the%20poor%20and%20marginalised%2C%20in%20November%202023%2C%20he%20announced%20a%20one-time%20benefit%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20to%20the%2094%20lakh%20families%2C%20and%20also%20announced%20plans%20to%20increase%20reservations%20for%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20OBCs%20to%2065%25%2C%20(up%20from%2050%25%2C%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20capped%20at).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%20became%20the%20second%20state%20after%20Bihar%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fvijayawada%2Fandhra-caste-census-to-kick-off-today-2nd-state-to-go-for-it%2Farticleshow%2F106968056.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannounce%20plans%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20a%20caste%20survey%3B%20its%20survey%20began%20on%20January%2019%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPolitical%20parties%20including%20the%20Congress%20have%20also%20declared%20that%20they%20will%20conduct%20a%20country-wide%20caste%20census%20if%20they%20come%20into%20power%20after%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Census%202021%20got%20postponed%20indefinetly%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20%E2%80%94%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20first%20time%20in%20its%20150-year%20history%20that%20the%20decennial%20census%20exercise%20has%20been%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711203325000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30142939%2Fcyber-security-1923446_1280.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsocio-economic-and-caste-census-website-has-been-down-for-over-two-months-now-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%20Development%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20maintaining%20the%20portal%20%E2%80%93%20quoted%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%20reasons%E2%80%9D%20when%20The%20Indian%20Express%20contacted%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsocio-economic-and-caste-census-website-has-been-down-for-over-two-months-now-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Backlash%2C%20Army%20Cancels%20Unprecedented%20Seminar%20on%20UCC%26nbsp%3Bin%26nbsp%3BKashmir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F23192915%2FArmy-in-Kashmir-II.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20An%20upcoming%20seminar%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%20on%20%E2%80%98uniform%20civil%20code%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Kashmir%20has%20run%20into%20rough%20weather%2C%20with%20former%20chief%20ministers%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20a%20retired%20army%20officer%20among%20others%20urging%20the%20force%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdivisive%20issue%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20uproar%2C%20the%20Army%20said%20on%20Saturday%20(March%2023)%20that%20the%20seminar%20had%20been%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Legal%20Awareness%20Seminar%20on%20March%2026%20by%20Kashmir%20Jurist%20in%20Kashmir%20University%20has%20been%20cancelled%20due%20to%20implementation%20of%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srinagar-based%20defence%20spokesman%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20Manoj%20Sahu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20is%20keen%20to%20implement%20the%20uniform%20civil%20code%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20is%20dubbed%20by%20many%20as%20a%20last%20straw%20in%20Indian%20secularism%20and%20the%20seminar%20in%20Kashmir%20was%20being%20seen%20as%20yet%20another%20attempt%20by%20the%20saffron%20party%20to%20use%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20armed%20forces%20for%20political%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one-day%20seminar%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Navigating%20Legal%20Frontiers%3A%20Understanding%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%202023%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Quest%20for%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20being%20organised%20by%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20HQ%2031%20Sub%20Area%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20auditorium%20and%20was%20scheduled%20for%20March%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20asked%20whether%20it%20was%20appropriate%20for%20the%20Army%20to%20debate%20the%20uniform%20civil%20code%20%E2%80%9Cand%20that%20too%20in%20a%20sensitive%20area%20like%20Kashmir%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20reason%20the%20Indian%20Army%20has%20remained%20apolitical%20%26amp%3B%20areligious.%20This%20ill-advised%20UCC%20seminar%20is%20a%20threat%20to%20both%20these%20basic%20tenets.%20Going%20ahead%20with%20this%20risks%20opening%20up%20the%20army%20to%20charges%20of%20getting%20involved%20in%20the%20murky%20world%20of%20politics%20coupled%20with%20interfering%20in%20religious%20matters%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Lieutenant%20General%20Deependra%20Singh%20Hooda%2C%20who%20has%20headed%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20strategic%20Northern%20Command%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Army%20should%20stay%20away%20from%20political%20and%20religious%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20personal%20view%20is%20that%20any%20subject%20that%20has%20even%20the%20faintest%20whiff%20of%20politics%20or%20religion%20to%20it%20should%20be%20studiously%20avoided%20by%20the%20military%2C%20particularly%20in%20a%20public%20discussion%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lieutenant%20General%20Hooda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20seminar%20is%20not%20the%20first%20event%20of%20its%20kind%20organised%20by%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20which%20organises%20regular%20sports%20and%20other%20events%20involving%20educational%20institutions%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20it%20was%20perhaps%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20Army%20was%20directly%20sponsoring%20an%20event%20on%20a%20political%20topic%20and%20that%20too%20at%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20most%20prestigious%20higher%20educational%20institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjai%20Sahni%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Institute%20for%20Conflict%20Management%2C%20a%20New%20Delhi-based%20think-tank%2C%20termed%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20decision%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHad%20this%20been%20a%20closed%20discussion%20to%20promote%20awareness%20among%20officers%2C%20it%20may%20have%20been%20a%20different%20matter.%20Such%20participation%20%E2%80%93%20indeed%20sponsorship%20of%20the%20event%20%E2%80%93%20bodes%20ill%20for%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20institutional%20culture%20and%20long%20established%20traditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sahni%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20and%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20president%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20military%20is%20the%20fourth%20strongest%20and%20one%20of%20the%20most%20disciplined%20forces%20in%20the%20world.%20But%20since%20%5Bthe%5D%20BJP%20has%20weaponised%20religion%20and%20is%20infiltrating%20it%20into%20all%20sacred%20institutions%20of%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Army%20seems%20to%20be%20yet%20another%20casualty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20invitation%20letter%20sent%20out%20on%20Friday%2C%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Ladakh%20high%20court%2C%20Justice%20N.%20Kotiswar%20Singh%2C%20was%20going%20to%20be%20the%20chief%20guest%20while%20Achal%20Sethi%2C%20law%20secretary%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Major%20General%20P.B.S.%20Lamba%2C%20who%20is%20the%20GoC%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20HQ%2031%20Sub%20Area%2C%20were%20among%20the%20panelists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20program%20was%20set%20to%20include%20a%20panel%20discussion%20on%20how%20the%20new%20code%20%E2%80%9Caligns%20with%20the%20principles%20of%20secularism%20and%20%E2%80%A6%20social%20harmony%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccontribute(s)%20to%20upholding%20individual%20rights%20and%20freedoms%E2%80%9D%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20to%20discuss%20the%20%E2%80%9Cchallenges%20and%20benefits%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%20for%20%E2%80%9Cfamily%20law%20and%20inheritance%20laws%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20invitation%20letter%20stated%20that%20a%20second%20panel%20discussion%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20seminar%20would%20focus%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Bharatiya%20Nayay%20Sanhita%202023%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20replaced%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%201860%2C%20and%20how%20the%20recent%20amendments%20to%20the%20IPC%20had%20led%20to%20%E2%80%9Cempowering%20and%20protecting%20the%20rights%20of%20crime%20victims%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20panel%20discussions%20were%20going%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20Q%26amp%3BA%20sessions%2C%20according%20to%20the%20invitation%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20was%20recently%20under%20the%20spotlight%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20over%20the%20alleged%20torture%20of%20civilians%20in%20Poonch%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20persons%2C%20who%20had%20suffered%20serious%20injuries%20during%20torture%2C%20later%20succumbed%20to%20their%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20the%20torture%20had%20also%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20recently%20asked%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Caravan%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine%20to%20pull%20down%20a%20story%20on%20the%20Poonch%20torture%20that%20had%20detailed%20how%20the%20Army%20abducted%20the%20civilians%20from%20their%20villages%20and%20later%20paid%20blood%20money%20to%20the%20victims%E2%80%99%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711201237000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F23192915%2FArmy-in-Kashmir-II.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fafter-backlash-army-scraps-its-ucc-seminar-in-kashmir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20was%20perhaps%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20Army%20was%20directly%20sponsoring%20an%20event%20on%20a%20political%20topic%2C%20and%20that%20too%20at%20Kashmir%E2%80%9