a%20community%2C%20so%20it%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20step%20up%20to%20safeguard%20it.%20We%20need%20to%20take%20more%20responsibility%20and%20consciously%20increase%20our%20awareness%20against%20forest%20fires.%20In%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20bust%20myths%20among%20villagers%20and%20reduce%20extreme%20forest%20fire%20incidences%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pritam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20could%20do%20it%2C%20then%20you%20too%20can.%20This%20Forest%20Day%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20pledge%20to%20save%20our%20jungles!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20The%20Hans%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fukhand-loses-highest-561-2-ha-green-cover-in-24hrs-to-fires-over-2k-ha-so-far%2Farticleshow%2F91136591.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUttarakhand%20loses%20highest%20561.2%20ha%20green%20cover%20in%2024%20hours%20to%20fires%3B%20over%202%2C000%20ha%20so%20far%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%3A%20by%20Shivani%20Azad%20for%20The%20Times%20of%20India%2C%20Published%20on%2028%20April%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffsi.nic.in%2Fisfr19%2Fvol2%2Fisfr-2019-vol-ii-uttarakhand.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20State%20of%20Forest%20Report%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20Forest%20Survey%20of%20India%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%2C%20Published%20in%202019.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711026101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1711021711.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Community-driven%20efforts%20led%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20in%20Uttarakhand%20have%20effectively%20reduced%20forest%20fire%20incidents%20in%201%2C000%20villages%20amidst%20rising%20cases%20due%20to%20climate%20change%20and%20human%20activities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345435%2Fyouth-fight-forest-fires-in-uttarakhand-the-hans-foundation-initiative-save-jungles%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%207%20Women-Led%20Startups%20of%20India%20Are%20Driving%20Impact%20at%20Scale%20in%20Climate%20Action%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20sponsored%20by%20Villgro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20it%20culinary%2C%20cosmetics%2C%20green%20energy%2C%20or%20agriculture%2C%20women%20have%20created%20a%20niche%20in%20every%20sector%20of%20the%20Indian%20market.%20According%20to%20a%20WISER%20%E2%80%94%20Women%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Startup%20Ecosystem%20Report%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345065%2Fhow-to-find-a-lawyer-legal-startup-pune-shreya-sharma-divorce-family-court-business-property-law-rent-agreement%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen-led%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20risen%20to%2018%20percent%20in%20the%20country%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20But%20while%20this%20is%20a%20poster%20story%20of%20the%20success%20that%20the%20female%20entrepreneurial%20world%20has%20witnessed%2C%20another%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EDealStreetAsia%3C%2Fem%3E%20claims%20that%20startups%20founded%20by%20women%20received%20only%200.3%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20venture%20capital%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20growth%20is%20a%20series%20of%20small%20steps%2C%20Cisco%20and%20Villgro%20%E2%80%94%20a%20social%20enterprise%20incubator%20%E2%80%94%20have%20come%20up%20with%20a%20joint%20initiative%2C%20%E2%80%98Tvaran%E2%80%99%2C%20whose%20intent%20is%20to%20introduce%20progressive%20changes%20to%20the%20way%20women-led%20startups%20are%20being%20empowered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20first%20cohort%2C%20launched%20in%20October%202022%2C%20met%20its%20goal%20of%20accelerating%20women%20entrepreneurs%20driving%20innovative%20solutions%20in%20the%20climate%20action%20sector%20by%20providing%20them%20access%20to%20markets%20and%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20specifically%20climate%20action%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kalyani%20Krishna%2C%20Manager%2C%20Gender%20Inclusion%20Villgro%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman-induced%20climate%20change%20is%20not%20just%20hearsay%2C%20she%20cautions.%20A%202020%20research%20initiative%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20Center%20for%20Climate%20Change%20Research%20(CCCR)%20in%20India%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Earth%20Sciences%20(MoES)%20revealed%20a%20rise%20of%200.7%20degrees%20Celsius%20surface%20air%20temperature%20from%201901%20to%202018%20and%20a%20rise%20of%201%20degree%20Celsius%20sea%20surface%20temperatures%20in%20the%20tropical%20Indian%20Ocean%20from%201951%20to%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20climate%20action%20startups%2C%20you%20ask%3F%20Why%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%20She%20emphasises%20how%20Tvaran%20is%20tying%20two%20goals%20into%20one%20by%20backing%20women%20business%20owners%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20champions%20of%20climate%20advocacy.%20Early-stage%20women%20entrepreneurs%20are%20being%20supported%20by%20helping%20them%20amplify%20their%20market%20presence.%20This%20is%20being%20achieved%20by%20giving%20them%20access%20to%20markets%20and%20finance%2C%20which%20will%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20help%20them%20commercialise%20and%20scale%20their%20ventures%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kalyani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201805px)%20100vw%2C%201805px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221805%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sectors%20where%20women%20are%20taking%20charge%20of%20businesses%20has%20expanded%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005.jpeg%201805w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-1536x2048.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345163%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222407%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20sectors%20where%20women%20are%20taking%20charge%20of%20businesses%20have%20expanded%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOffering%20the%20women%20assessment%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F51427%2F11-social-incubators-helping-indian-social-entrepreneurs-t