-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmomos-_11zon-1709902674-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmomos-_11zon-1709902674-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmomos-_11zon-1709902674-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344422%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Fomo%20Momo%20food%20truck%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20United%20States%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ankita%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20penchant%20for%20momos%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337833%2Fzomoz-startup-nit-engineer-innovated-automated-momo-machine-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etastiest%20momos%3C%2Fa%3E%20you%E2%80%99ve%20had%20in%20India%20have%20got%20to%20be%20the%20ones%20from%20Delhi%2C%20right%3F%E2%80%9D%20Ankita%20asks%20me%2C%20daring%20me%20to%20counter%20this.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20replied%20truthfully%2C%20seemingly%20pleasing%20her%20with%20the%20answer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20Ankita%20spent%20her%20weekends%20sampling%20street%20food%20across%20the%20bazaars%20of%20the%20national%20capital.%20But%20the%20momos%20remained%20her%20favourite.%20So%2C%20years%20later%2C%20when%20she%20met%20Impreet%20in%20the%20US%20at%20a%20dinner%20organised%20by%20their%20husbands%2C%20who%20are%20college%20friends%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20proclaimed%20her%20love%20for%20momos%2C%20Ankita%20knew%20she%20had%20found%20her%20food%20soulmate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20that%20conversation%20that%20gave%20us%20the%20idea%20of%20bringing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342261%2Fwoman-entrepreneu