t%20experience%20any%20improvement.%20A%20doctor%20advised%20her%20to%20visit%20a%20hospital%20in%20Dehradun%20for%20better%20access%20to%20treatment%2C%20which%20involved%20travelling%20almost%20four%20hours%20to%20cover%20a%20distance%20of%20over%20150%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20Government-aided%20hospital%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20Chandrakala%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F140950%2Findian-scientists-develop-sensor-for-early-detection-of-chronic-kidney-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echronic%20kidney%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20advised%20dialysis%20twice%20a%20week.%20As%20this%20treatment%20was%20not%20available%20near%20her%20residence%2C%20she%20had%20to%20travel%20to%20Dehradun%20and%20stay%20there%20for%20two%20nights%20every%20week%20to%20get%20the%20dialysis%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20single%20mother%2C%20being%20separated%20from%20her%20son%2C%20spending%20on%20travel%2C%20and%20eight%20nights%20at%20lodging%20every%20month%2C%20was%20much%20more%20than%20what%20she%20could%20afford%2C%20both%20physically%20and%20mentally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20faced%20by%20the%20ASHA%20worker%20resonates%20with%20many%20residing%20in%20rural%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EGlobal%20Burden%20of%20Disease%20(GBD)%202015%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Chronic%20Kidney%20Disease%20(CKD)%20ranks%20as%20the%20eighth%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20in%20India%2C%20largely%20because%20many%20patients%20develop%20complications%20leading%20to%20end-stage%20renal%20disease.%20A%20report%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lancet%3C%2Fem%3E%20estimated%20that%20two%20lakh%20people%20in%20India%20develop%20end-stage%20renal%20disease%20every%20year%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250227%2Fshashank-moddhia-mumbai-startup-renal-project-affordable-kidney-dialysis-in-india-healthcare-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccess%20to%20long-term%20dialysis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20costs%20associated%20with%20dialysis%20care%20add%20to%20the%20financial%20woes%20of%20patients.%20Collaborating%20with%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Government%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20identified%20renal%20care%20as%20a%20major%20gap.%20Noticing%20that%20many%20residents%20in%20hilly%20areas%20were%20forced%20to%20migrate%20to%20Dehradun%20or%20Haldwani%20for%20dialysis%2C%20the%20organisation%20decided%20to%20bridge%20this%20gap%20by%20establishing%20last-mile%20availability%20of%20dialysis%20centres%20throughout%20the%20state%2C%20through%20the%20Hans%20Renal%20Care%20Centres%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20with%20a%20single%20centre%20in%20March%202022%2C%20the%20programme%20has%20now%20expanded%20to%20include%20over%2027%20centres%20across%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Punjab.%20Over%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20THF%20has%20helped%20over%204%2C000%20patients%20access%20free%20dialysis%20through%20these%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201188px)%20100vw%2C%201188px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-14-093810_11zon-1710411627.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221188%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hans%20Foundation%20has%20established%20last-mile%20availability%20of%20dialysis%20centres%20throughout%20the%20state%20through%20the%20Hans%20Renal%20Care%20Centres%20initiative.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-14-093810_11zon-1710411627.jpg%201188w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-14-093810_11zon-1710411627-300x156.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupload